---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — STOA Platform"
  description="Privacy Policy for STOA Platform. How we handle your data, analytics, and communications."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            STOA Platform is an open-source API management project maintained by CAB Ingenierie, a French consulting company.
            This policy covers the website <strong>gostoa.dev</strong> and associated services
            (portal.gostoa.dev, console.gostoa.dev, docs.gostoa.dev).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p><strong>Website analytics:</strong> We use Vercel Analytics to collect anonymous, aggregated page view data. No cookies are set. No personal data is collected by analytics.</p>
          <p><strong>Newsletter:</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter (via Buttondown), we store your email address to send updates. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>
          <p><strong>Portal / Console accounts:</strong> When you create an account on portal.gostoa.dev, we collect your email and name via Keycloak (self-hosted authentication). This data is stored on European infrastructure (OVH, France).</p>
          <p><strong>Contact forms:</strong> Emails sent to hello@gostoa.dev, demo@gostoa.dev, or sales@gostoa.dev are processed by our team and not shared with third parties.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>Provide and improve the STOA Platform services</li>
            <li>Send product updates (newsletter subscribers only)</li>
            <li>Respond to demo requests and support inquiries</li>
            <li>Generate anonymous usage statistics</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
          <p>
            All platform data is hosted on European infrastructure (OVH GRA9, Hetzner FSN1).
            Authentication is managed by self-hosted Keycloak. Secrets are managed via self-hosted Infisical.
            No data is stored on US-based cloud providers for production services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-400 mt-2">
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
            <li>Object to processing</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:privacy@gostoa.dev" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">privacy@gostoa.dev</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            gostoa.dev does not use tracking cookies. Vercel Analytics is cookie-free.
            Authentication sessions on portal/console use secure, HTTP-only session cookies strictly necessary for the service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy-related questions:
            <a href="mailto:privacy@gostoa.dev" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">privacy@gostoa.dev</a>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            CAB Ingenierie — France
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
